---
import TestPage from "../layouts/TestPage.astro";
---

<TestPage
  title="Soluciones Digitales – Guía de Inicio"
  heading="Encuentra la Solución que tu Finca Necesita"
  description="Nuestra tecnología se adapta a tu perfil para ofrecerte las herramientas exactas que necesitas en tu día a día."
  variant="solutions"
  layoutType="mosaic"
  heroSectionClass="hero-soluciones-offset"
  bodySectionClass="page-body--soluciones"
  mosaicImages={["/images/soluciones/mobile_app_field.png", "/images/soluciones/campo_olivos_real.png"]}
>
  <div class="subpage-content">
    <section class="solutions-intro">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="feature-detail glass">
          <h2>Impulsando la Transformación del Sector</h2>
          <p>
            En el entorno agrario actual, la digitalización ya no es una opción, es una necesidad para la rentabilidad y el cumplimiento normativo. Nuestras soluciones están diseñadas para eliminar la carga administrativa y maximizar la eficiencia en el campo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-image">
          <img src="/images/soluciones/sensor_campo_inteligente.png" alt="Sensor inteligente en campo" class="sol-img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="value-proposition grid-3">
      <div class="value-item feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card__badge">Beneficios Clave</div>
        <div class="value-item__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"></line><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"></line><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Toma de Decisiones</h3>
        <p>Datos reales para decidir cuándo regar, abonar o cosechar con precisión quirúrgica.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card__badge">Beneficios Clave</div>
        <div class="value-item__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"></path><path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"></path><path d="M7 21h10"></path><path d="M12 3v18"></path><path d="M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seguridad Legal</h3>
        <p>Garantizamos que todos tus registros cumplen al 100% con la normativa SIEX vigente.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item feature-card">
        <div class="feature-card__badge">Beneficios Clave</div>
        <div class="value-item__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"></path><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C10 14.5 10.5 13 12 13s2 1.5 2 2.75"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sostenibilidad</h3>
        <p>Optimiza el uso de recursos y reduce el impacto ambiental de tu explotación.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-selector">
      <h2 class="text-center">Selecciona tu perfil para comenzar</h2>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="feature-card feature-card--premium">
          <div class="feature-card__badge">Más popular</div>
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Soy Agricultor</h3>
          <p>
            Controla tu cosecha desde el móvil. Gestiona stock, registra labores y visualiza alarmas de tus sensores en una sola app.
          </p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>✓ Cuaderno de campo móvil</li>
            <li>✓ Alertas de riego y heladas</li>
            <li>✓ Trazabilidad automática</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/soluciones/agricultores" class="cta-btn">Ver Herramientas</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card feature-card--premium">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Soy Técnico o Asesor</h3>
          <p>
            Escala tu servicio de asesoría. Supervisa múltiples fincas, valida tratamientos y genera informes oficiales en segundos.
          </p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>✓ Gestión multiexplotación</li>
            <li>✓ Validación SIEX en lote</li>
            <li>✓ Reportes exportables</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/soluciones/tecnicos" class="cta-btn">Explorar Panel</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</TestPage>

<style>
  :global(.page-hero.hero-soluciones-offset) {
    min-height: 400px;
    padding-top: 10px !important;
    padding-bottom: 22px !important;
  }

  :global(.page-hero.hero-soluciones-offset::before) {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 24%, rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.12), transparent 24%),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.28) 0%, rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.08) 45%, rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.32) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .page-hero__container) {
    z-index: 2;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic) {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(320px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 42px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__content) {
    padding: 26px 28px 24px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    background: rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.34);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 76px -40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__content::before) {
    content: "SOLUCIONES";
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.14);
    border: 1px solid rgba(29, 185, 154, 0.24);
    color: #bff3e8;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic h1) {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    max-width: 11ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__desc-row) {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-top: 0 !important;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__desc-row p) {
    margin: 0 !important;
    max-width: 54ch;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.76;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-cta) {
    justify-self: start;
    margin: 0 !important;
    padding: 13px 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__images) {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.92fr;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 320px;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img) {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 320px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #0b1a14;
    background-size: cover !important;
    background-position: center !important;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 28px 68px -38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img::after) {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.02), rgba(7, 16, 13, 0.28));
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img--1) {
    transform: translateY(18px);
    background-position: center 68% !important;
    background-size: 108% auto !important;
  }

  :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img--2) {
    min-height: 270px;
    transform: translateY(-14px);
  }

  :global(.page-body.page-body--soluciones) {
    padding-bottom: 2px !important;
  }

  .solutions-intro {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }

  .sol-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .intro-image:hover .sol-img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .value-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .value-item__icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: var(--color-turquoise);
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .value-item p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .profile-selector {
    padding: 40px 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .profile-selector h2 {
    margin-bottom: 35px;
  }

  .profile-selector .cards-grid {
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  .subpage-content > :last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .subpage-content {
    padding-bottom: 0 !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .subpage-content .feature-card:last-child,
  .subpage-content .cards-grid:last-child,
  .subpage-content .profile-selector:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .feature-card--premium {
    position: relative;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card--premium:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-turquoise);
  }

  .feature-card__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 20px;
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: white;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .feature-list {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    :global(.page-hero.hero-soluciones-offset) {
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 0 !important;
      padding-bottom: 28px !important;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__content) {
      padding: 24px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__content::before) {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic h1) {
      max-width: none;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__desc-row p) {
      max-width: none;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-cta) {
      justify-self: center;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .hero-mosaic__images) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img),
    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img--2) {
      min-height: 200px;
      transform: none;
    }

    :global(.hero-soluciones-offset .m-img--1) {
      background-position: center 66% !important;
      background-size: 112% auto !important;
    }

    :global(.page-body.page-body--soluciones) {
      padding-bottom: 20px !important;
    }

    .intro-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .feature-detail {
      order: 1; /* Title and text on top */
      text-align: center;
    }

    .intro-image {
      order: 2; /* Image on bottom */
    }

    .value-item {
      text-align: center; /* Center these items */
    }

    .value-item__icon {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .feature-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature-list li {
      justify-content: center;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    /* Force the large profile cards to stack vertically on mobile */
    .profile-selector .cards-grid {
      display: grid !important;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      gap: 30px !important;
    }
  }
</style>

